title: Mishka Tofino, BC show
description: The O'Neill Cold Water Classic Tour featuring Mishka officially starts this Thursday at the Legion in Tofino, BC. Mishka's performance will be the official O'Neill Cold Water Classic Canada party. Tickets are available at The Legion box office.
